# `Vertex vertex(num x, num y)`         
# `Vertex vertex(num x, num y, Figure marker)`

Synopsis:

Description: A Vertex is a coordinate pair used in [shape]s.
Coordinates are given relative to the (0,0) origin at the left bottom of a shape.
Optionally, a figure `marker` may be given that will be drawn on these coordinates.

